{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_014cYqs1ZrBcCUkzHmgHpD2k","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Only 1 pod has been created so far. The StatefulSet creates pods sequentially - it won't create es-cluster-1 until es-cluster-0 is Ready, but es-cluster-0 can't be Ready until all 3 nodes form the cluster. This is a bootstrap deadlock.\n\nWait, that's not quite right. The StatefulSet default behavior (`podManagementPolicy: OrderedReady`) waits for each pod to be Ready before creating the next one. For ES, the readiness probe is checking for cluster health (green/yellow), which requires all 3 master nodes to be up. This creates a chicken-and-egg problem.\nI need to switch to `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` so all three pods spin up at once, and I should also relax the readiness probe during initial bootstrap so the cluster can form. I'll need to delete and recreate the StatefulSet since `podManagementPolicy` can't be patched after creation.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":448,"cache_read_input_tokens":47874,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":448},"output_tokens":28,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0406e1a2-236f-48f3-a2b3-94bc9a85fba7","uuid":"02cf203b-c543-4b30-9342-ba7aa1ef7f45","request_id":"req_011Ccer9n2x392BBfozkqoGX"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_014cYqs1ZrBcCUkzHmgHpD2k","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The StatefulSet uses `OrderedReady` by default — it won't create `es-cluster-1` until `es-cluster-0` is Ready, but the cluster can't be healthy with only 1 of 3 master nodes. I need to switch to `Parallel` pod management to break this deadlock."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":448,"cache_read_input_tokens":47874,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":448},"output_tokens":28,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0406e1a2-236f-48f3-a2b3-94bc9a85fba7","uuid":"4f2187ff-078b-4f6d-8a77-eec4082fe659","request_id":"req_011Ccer9n2x392BBfozkqoGX"}
